reviewText: Lovelovelove

For people who enjoy watching Keeping Up, I would highly recommend it. I don't have cable, so watching it through Amazon is a great idea. The quality is good, and I never have any problems running the shows.
Of the seasons I've seen, season 4 was likely my favorite. My favorite episodes include Kim getting her new dog off the street, the family going to Vegas and Scott getting drunk and causing problems, and the episode where they did the charity boxing. Good entertainment compared to what's out there. For those who enjoy the show, highly recommended!

These girls are very smart.  Also having your mom as a momager is great!  Kris really knows what she is doing and for everything they have out there you can't tell me that these girls are stupid.  Look where they are and then look where we are.  We are not on dvd's like them and that would be because they might be just a little smarter.  Good looks and brains can go a long way.
